HTMONITORING


HTMonitoring is a web interface for viewing Hyper Table stats.
It read from rrds and stats.txt files.

Please provide the dir for rrd files in config/config.yml


INSTALL
This app requires ruby bindings for rrd to be installed

gem install sinatra rack json titleize



to start the server

1) htm-app start ( it will start in daemonize mode)
2) rackup config.ru -p 3000



TO-DOS

1) proper error handling
2) show user friendly errors
3) add stop to htm-app
4) add line graph with timelines

